                <ANNOTATION_VALUE>ṭaḥana hina yḥuṭṭ-ha bi-nafs il-gūmgūm yaʕni miṯil, ḥagg muxaṣṣaṣ il-gahwa, zayy kiḏa</ANNOTATION_VALUE>
