                <ANNOTATION_VALUE>kull il-ʕālim li ḥōl-a, l-ḥarīm w ir-riǧāl kullu "ō kwayyis kwayyis", rāḥ hū iḏbaḥ-a w ǧā</ANNOTATION_VALUE>
